      "csl:pageColumn": "3,1",
      "rdf:value": "<L>423<pc>3,1<k1>akz<k2>akz<e>1\r\n<s>akz</s> ¦ (perhaps a kind of old <ab>Desid.</ab> of √ <hom>1.</hom> <s>aS</s>) <ab>cl.</ab> 1. 5. <s>akzati</s>, <s>akzRoti</s> (<ls>Pāṇ. iii, 1, 75</ls>; <ab>fut.</ab> <s>akzizyati</s> or <s>akzyati</s>, <ls>L.</ls>; <ab>aor.</ab> <s>AkzIt</s>, 3. <ab>du.</ab> <s>AkzizwAm</s> or <s>AzwAm</s>, <ls>L.</ls>; <ab>perf.</ab> <s>Anakza</s> [<ls>Pāṇ. vii, 4, 60</ls> <ab>Comm.</ab>], but <ab>Ā.</ab> <ab>p.</ab> [with the Vedic weak stem <s>Akz</s> <ab>cf.</ab> <ab>perf.</ab> <s>AS-uH</s> 3. <ab>pl.</ab> &c. <ab>fr.</ab> √ <hom>1.</hom> <s>aS</s>] <s>AkzARa/</s>),\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to reach, <ls>RV. x, 22, 11</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to pass through, penetrate, pervade, embrace, <ls>L.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to accumulate (to form the cube?), <ls>L.</ls> :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Caus.</ab> <s>akzayati</s>, <s>Acikzat</s>, to cause to pervade, <ls>L.</ls> :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Desid.</ab> <s>acikzizati</s> or <s>acikzati</s>, <ls>L.</ls><info whitneyroots=\"akz1,1;akz2,1\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1,5\"/><listinfo n=\"sup\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3Aakz#record-pwg",
