      "csl:pageColumn": "1-0013",
      "rdf:value": "<L>165<pc>1-0013<k1>akz<k2>akz\n{#akz#}¦, {#a/kzati#} und {#akzRo/ti#}\n<ls>P. 3,1,75.</ls>\n<ls>VOP. 8,74.</ls> {#Anakza#}\n<ls>P. 7,4,60</ls>, <is>Vārtt</is>. 1. {#akzitA#} und {#azwA; akzizyati#} und {#akzyati; AkzIt, AkzizwAm#} oder {#AzwAm#}\n<ls>VOP. 8,75.</ls> {#akzitvA#} oder {#azwvA; azwa#} .\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) {%erreichen, treffen%}: {#ma\\kzU tA ta^ indra dA\\nApna^sa AkzA\\Re#} (<ab>d. i.</ab> {#AnAkzARe) SU^ra vajrivaH . yadDa\\ SuzRa^sya da\\mBayo^ jA\\taM viSva^M sa\\yAva^BiH ..#}\n<ls>ṚV. 10,22,11.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) {%durchdringen, erfüllen%} ({#vyAptO#})\n<ls>DHĀTUP.</ls> <ls>NAIGH. 2,18.</ls> ({#A\\kzA\\RaH#}).\n<div n=\"1\">— 3) {%anhäufen%} ({#saMGAte#})\n<ls>DHĀTUP.</ls> — <ab>Caus.</ab> {#akzayati, Acikzat#} . — <ab>Desid.</ab> {#acikzizati#} und {#acikzati#} .\n<div n=\"v\">— <ab>Vgl.</ab> {#aS#} .\n<div n=\"p\">— {#nis#} {%zerstreuen, aus einander jagen%}: {#i\\mami^ndra varDaya kza\\triya^M ma i\\maM vi\\SAme^kavf\\zaM kf^Ru\\ tvam . nira\\mitrA^~ akzRuhyasya\\ sarvA\\~stAnra^nDayAsmA ahamu\\ttarezu^ ..#}\n<ls>AV. 4,22,1.</ls>\n<div n=\"p\">— {#sam#} {%durchgehen, durchwandern%}: {#tvaM devi brahmalokaM samakzase#} (Med.)\n<ls>R. 2,52,80.</ls>\n<LEND>"
    },
